---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Pricing — Pay by the Hour, No Membership | Tennis Terminal"
  description="Tennis from $32/hr with the ball machine included; pickleball from $24/hr for up to four players. Credit packs and an off-peak pass. No membership, ever."
  path="/pricing"
>
  <section style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,84px) 24px clamp(24px,4vw,40px);text-align:center">
    <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);margin-bottom:16px">Pricing</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(38px,5.4vw,60px);line-height:1.04;max-width:18ch;margin:0 auto">Pay for the time you play. Nothing else.</h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:clamp(17px,2.2vw,20px);line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin:20px auto 0;max-width:52ch;text-wrap:pretty">Prices depend on your sport — tennis is a solo, ball-machine session; pickleball splits one bay up to four. No membership, no joining fee, ever.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- CARDS -->
  <section style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(16px,3vw,32px) 24px clamp(24px,4vw,40px)">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:22px;align-items:stretch">
      <!-- TENNIS -->
      <div style="background:var(--tt-court-ink);border-radius:18px;padding:34px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(22,59,42,0.18)">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px">
          <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-court-ink);background:var(--tt-ball-yellow);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:999px">Tennis</span>
          <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);opacity:0.65">Solo practice</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:28px;margin-top:26px;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-ball-yellow)">Off-peak</div><div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:3px;margin-top:6px"><span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:46px;color:var(--tt-honey-cream)">$32</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);opacity:0.7">/hr</span></div></div>
          <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-marigold)">Peak</div><div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:3px;margin-top:6px"><span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:46px;color:var(--tt-honey-cream)">$50</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);opacity:0.7">/hr</span></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="height:1px;background:rgba(253,246,230,0.15);margin:24px 0"></div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start"><span style="color:var(--tt-ball-yellow);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700">✓</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-honey-cream)">Ball machine included — speed, spin &amp; feed from your phone</span></div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);opacity:0.75;margin-top:14px">Just you and the machine. One honest number — never an upsell at checkout.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- PICKLEBALL -->
      <div style="background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:18px;padding:34px;display:flex;flex-direction:column">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px">
          <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-primary-on);background:var(--tt-play-green);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:999px">Pickleball</span>
          <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-ink-300)">Up to 4 players</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:28px;margin-top:26px;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green)">Off-peak</div><div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:3px;margin-top:6px"><span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:46px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">$24</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-ink-500)">/hr</span></div></div>
          <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-marigold)">Peak</div><div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:3px;margin-top:6px"><span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:46px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">$38</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-ink-500)">/hr</span></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="height:1px;background:var(--tt-border);margin:24px 0"></div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start"><span style="color:var(--tt-play-green);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700">+</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">Ball machine optional — add for solo drilling, <strong style="color:var(--tt-court-ink)">+$8/hr</strong></span></div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-500);margin-top:14px">Split one bay up to four ways — same price whether it's two of you or a full game.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SAVE MORE -->
  <section style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px clamp(40px,6vw,64px)">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px"><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green)">Play more, save more</div></div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:18px;align-items:stretch">
      <div style="background:var(--tt-white);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:16px;padding:28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:19px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">Starter credit pack</div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px;margin-top:14px"><span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:34px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">$200</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-play-green);font-weight:600">$220 to spend</span></div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-500);margin-top:10px">10% bonus credit. Works across tennis and pickleball.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--tt-white);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:16px;padding:28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:19px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">Regular credit pack</div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px;margin-top:14px"><span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:34px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">$360</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-play-green);font-weight:600">$410 to spend</span></div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-500);margin-top:10px">~14% bonus credit. No expiry, no subscription.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--tt-play-green);border-radius:16px;padding:28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:19px;color:var(--tt-honey-cream)">Off-peak pass</div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:4px;margin-top:14px"><span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:34px;color:var(--tt-honey-cream)">$218</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);opacity:0.8">/mo</span></div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);opacity:0.9;margin-top:10px">Unlimited off-peak play, tennis or pickleball — one pass, any sport. Peak hours &amp; ball-machine add-ons not included.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED -->
  <section style="background:var(--tt-white);border-top:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-bottom:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade)">
    <div style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,84px) 24px">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:36px"><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);margin-bottom:14px">Always included</div><h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,3.8vw,40px);line-height:1.08">Free with every booking</h2></div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:14px">
        <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px"><span style="color:var(--tt-play-green);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:18px">✓</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">Loaner racquets &amp; paddles</span></div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px"><span style="color:var(--tt-play-green);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:18px">✓</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">Balls for both sports</span></div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px"><span style="color:var(--tt-play-green);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:18px">✓</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">Up to 4 players (pickleball)</span></div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px"><span style="color:var(--tt-play-green);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:18px">✓</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">Free cancellation, 12hr out</span></div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px"><span style="color:var(--tt-play-green);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:18px">✓</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">Water filling station</span></div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px"><span style="color:var(--tt-play-green);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:18px">✓</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">A private bay, just your group</span></div>
      </div>
      <p style="text-align:center;font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-ink-500);margin-top:28px">Planning something bigger? <a href="/events">See event &amp; buyout pricing →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,80px) 24px;text-align:center">
    <h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,40px);line-height:1.1">No membership. No catch.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:14px">Join the waitlist and your first hour's on us when we open.</p>
    <a href="/join" style="display:inline-block;font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:16px;color:var(--color-primary-on);background:var(--tt-play-green);padding:15px 30px;border-radius:10px;margin-top:26px">Join the waitlist →</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
